'''氧化锎'''是[[锎|锎]]的一种[[氧化物|氧化物]]，[[化学式|化学式]] Cf<sub>2</sub>O<sub>3</sub>。由于所有[[锎的同位素|锎的同位素]]都是人造的，氧化锎也不存在于自然界。

== 性质==
氧化锎是一种黄绿色固体，熔点 1750 °C<ref name="HOWI_1972"/>。它是体心立方晶系的，晶格参数为 ''a'' = 1083.9 ± 0.4 [[皮米|pm]]。<ref name="CF_OX_CL_1967">J. L. Green, B. B. Cunningham: ''Crystallography of the Compounds of Californium. I. Crystal Structure and Lattice Parameters of Californium Sesquioxide and Californium Trichloride'', in: ''[[Inorg._Nucl._Chem._Lett.|Inorg. Nucl. Chem. Lett.]]'', '''1967''', ''3'' (9), S. 343–349 ([[doi:10.1016/0020-1650(67)80040-0|doi:10.1016/0020-1650(67)80040-0]]).</ref><ref name="CF_OX_CL_1969">J. C. Copeland, B. B. Cunningham: ''Crystallography of the Compounds of Californium. II. Crystal Structure and Lattice Parameters of Californium Oxychloride and Californium Sesquioxide'', in: ''[[J._Inorg._Nucl._Chem.|J. Inorg. Nucl. Chem.]]'', '''1969''', ''31'' (3), S. 733–740 ([[doi:10.1016/0022-1902(69)80020-5|doi:10.1016/0022-1902(69)80020-5]]).</ref> 立方和单斜的 Cf<sub>2</sub>O<sub>3</sub> 的转变温度为 1400 °C。<ref name="CF_OX">R. D. Baybarz, R. G. Haire, J. A. Fahey: ''On the Californium Oxide System'', in: ''[[J._Inorg._Nucl._Chem.|J. Inorg. Nucl. Chem.]]'', '''1972''', ''34'' (2), S. 557–565 ([[doi:10.1016/0022-1902(72)80435-4|doi:10.1016/0022-1902(72)80435-4]]).</ref>

它的[[标准生成焓|标准生成焓]]在 25 °C 是 −1652.6 ± 10.3 [[焦耳|kJ]]•mol<sup>−1</sup>。<ref name="Enthalpie">Lester R. Morss, J. Fuger, J. Goffart, N. Edelstein, G. V. Shalimoff: ''Enthalpy of Formation and Magnetic Susceptibility of Californium Sesquioxide, Cf<sub>2</sub>O<sub>3</sub>'', in: ''[[Journal_of_the_Less_Common_Metals|Journal of the Less Common Metals]]'', '''1987''', ''127'', S. 251–257 ([[doi:10.1016/0022-5088(87)90385-7|doi:10.1016/0022-5088(87)90385-7]]).</ref>

== 用处==
它可以用来制作 <sup>252</sup>Cf-中子源。首先，<sup>252</sup>Cf(III) 会被做成草酸盐 (Cf<sub>2</sub>(C<sub>2</sub>O<sub>4</sub>)<sub>3</sub>) ，然后分解形成氧化锎。<ref name="Patent_3627691">United States Patent 3627691: [http://www.freepatentsonline.com/3627691.html ''A Method of Preparing a Californium-252 Neutron Source''] {{Wayback|url=http://www.freepatentsonline.com/3627691.html |date=20200920051203 }}.</ref>

